


is a station on the Tokyo Metro Hanz&lt;U+014D&gt;mon Line and the Toei &lt;U+014C&gt;edo Line in Koto, Tokyo, Japan.
Some trains on both lines terminate and originate at this station.
History

December 12, 2000 - &lt;U+014C&gt;edo Line station opens
March 19, 2003 - Hanz&lt;U+014D&gt;mon Line station opens

